on your foot

01:18:42.683 --> 01:18:44.340
and they're still standing on it

01:18:44.374 --> 01:18:46.722
and every time, again,
that wound gets opened

01:18:46.756 --> 01:18:50.346
when we, Ferguson...

01:18:50.380 --> 01:18:52.797
We all know what's in the news

01:18:52.831 --> 01:18:57.525
and so it's just a constant
reopening of an old wound

01:18:57.560 --> 01:19:01.046
that we are still just
incredibly impacted.

01:19:09.675 --> 01:19:11.919
