and I think we all are

01:19:42.916 --> 01:19:46.091
but it helps by us being
so close knit.

01:19:46.609 --> 01:19:50.647
[indistinct conversation]

01:19:51.234 --> 01:19:54.755
I'm going to fight to the end
to try to make

01:19:54.790 --> 01:19:56.688
everybody see what's going on.

01:19:58.552 --> 01:20:00.692
The silence need to be broken.

01:20:04.765 --> 01:20:09.528
We can't embed hate
into one another.

01:20:09.908 --> 01:20:14.568
I'm not going to
embed hate into my child.

01:20:16.432 --> 01:20:18.572
We need to have an
honest conversation.

01:20:18.606 --> 01:20:21.920
LAWSON-JONES:
We need to sit down and put
all of the issues on the table.

01:20:21.955 --> 01:20:25.751
Not just the things that
are fuzzy and feel good.

01:20:26.304 --> 01:20:28.720
