What I found in my research
and dealing with these families

01:22:12.824 --> 01:22:14.757
that come from
this manumission,

01:22:14.791 --> 01:22:18.761
all of them have this sense
of pride in their family,

01:22:18.795 --> 01:22:20.521
the sense of pride
in themselves

01:22:20.556 --> 01:22:22.385
and their work and what they do.

01:22:24.008 --> 01:22:27.459
DUCKENFIELD:
We obtained certain advantages
from being free people.

01:22:27.494 --> 01:22:29.945
If you look at
our family structure,

01:22:29.979 --> 01:22:31.360
it stayed pretty intact.

01:22:31.636 --> 01:22:33.638
We had two heads
of the household.

01:22:34.708 --> 01:22:37.711
LAWSON-JONES: It did in some
ways give us a head start

01:22:37.745 --> 01:22:41.577
in that we had to be
self-reliant

01:22:41.611 --> 01:22:45.961
far long before other people
of color were free.

01:22:46.409 --> 01:22:48.480
That gets instilled
into your family.

01:22:48.515 --> 01:22:50.758
It becomes a part
of who you are.

01:22:50.896 --> 01:22:52.726
You pass it on to your children
to their children,

01:22:52.760 --> 01:22:55.004
their children
and so on and so forth.

01:22:55.418 --> 01:22:58.663
[♪♪♪]

01:22:59.629 --> 01:23:01.977
POWELL: The hard nut of it
is really whites.

01:23:02.701 --> 01:23:06.843
So we had it exactly backwards
in terms of the Negro problem.

01:23:06.982 --> 01:23:08.949
We have a white problem
in the United States

01:23:08.984 --> 01:23:12.435
and I don't mean this
as a blame and whatever

01:23:12.470 --> 01:23:14.851
but I think people won't get
this on their own.

01:23:14.886 --> 01:23:16.646
It really takes a lot of work.

01:23:16.681 --> 01:23:20.926
This is so deeply in our DNA and
it's reflected in our politics,

01:23:20.961 --> 01:23:23.239
the way we do politics,
the way we do our economy

01:23:23.274 --> 01:23:25.000
and the way we think
about ourselves.

01:23:25.034 --> 01:23:27.933
But we actually need to give
birth to a new white identity,

01:23:27.968 --> 01:23:30.108
a white identity that
doesn't need to dominate,

01:23:30.143 --> 01:23:32.524
a white identity
that's not totally angst

01:23:32.559 --> 01:23:35.320
about being in connection
and relationship with the other,

01:23:35.355 --> 01:23:38.910
a white identity that recognizes
that it is the other.

01:23:39.186 --> 01:23:42.155
[♪♪♪]

01:23:42.845 --> 01:23:45.537
CAUSEY: But to do this,
we have to recognize

01:23:45.572 --> 01:23:49.334
that we as white people
have benefited enormously

01:23:49.369 --> 01:23:53.511
from our privilege at
the expense of other people.

01:23:54.029 --> 01:23:57.066
The cost of this prejudice
and inequality

01:23:57.101 --> 01:23:59.758
has come at far too high
a price.

01:24:00.414 --> 01:24:03.762
